no black bounty hunter before.

1832
02:18:41,793 --> 02:18:44,819
Black boy paid to kill white men?
How'd you like that line of work?

1833
02:18:45,897 --> 02:18:48,525
Probably pretty good while it lasted,
huh?

1834
02:18:50,569 --> 02:18:52,036
(sizzling)

1835
02:18:54,673 --> 02:18:56,641
(Django yells, muffled)

1836
02:18:56,775 --> 02:18:57,833
(grunting)

1837
02:18:57,976 --> 02:18:59,841
Time to say good night
to them nuts, blackie.

1838
02:18:59,978 --> 02:19:02,674
- (yelling)
- On three. One...

1839
02:19:02,814 --> 02:19:05,749
- (screaming)
- I got you. Two...

1840
02:19:05,884 --> 02:19:09,115
- (screaming)
- Calm down, now, here it comes.

1841
02:19:09,254 --> 02:19:11,848
- (screaming)
