1843
02:19:14,593 --> 02:19:18,529
Something to do
with the Old Man's funeral.

1844
02:19:18,664 --> 02:19:22,464
Oh, and she changed her mind
'bout snipping Django.

1845
02:19:23,268 --> 02:19:26,135
She gonna give him
to the LeQuint Dickey people.

1846
02:19:26,271 --> 02:19:27,795
(Django moaning)

1847
02:19:27,939 --> 02:19:30,066
Well, she didn't
waste a minute telling me.

1848
02:19:37,315 --> 02:19:39,112
How disappointing.

1849
02:19:45,624 --> 02:19:47,421
(hissing)

1850
